summary: Summon Wisp Mother can now be learned or bought from any trainer or spell merchant.
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://img89.imageshack.us/img89/2488/wispmotherl.jpg[/img][/center]

[u]Description[/u]
A simple spell that summons a Wisp Mother. I created this primarily for me a year ago, but by request I\'m uploading it. This spell is balanced.

[quote]JustChill, on 12 Mar 2013 - 10:43, said:
I noticed from a picture of yours that you created a mod to summon Whisp Mothers?
Would ya mind sharing that on the Nexus, or with me?[/quote]

Plugin includes:
- You can buy it from anyone who sells Spell Tomes.
- It can be found as loot.

[u]Install:[/u]
Place \"SummonWispMother.esp\" in your \\Skyrim\\Data\\ folder.

[u]Uninstall:[/u]
Delete \"SummonWispMother.esp\" 

[u]Credits:[/u]
Bethesda

[u]Conflicts:[/u] It will conflict with any mod that modifies [u]LItemSpellTomes25AllConjuration[/u]
Just use Wrye Bash to create a patch. The mod is cleaned using [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/25859]TES5Edit[/url].

- Aoikani
author: Aoikani
